{"title":"高级功能","markdown":{"headingText":"高级功能","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n## 多会话并行执行\n\n多会话模式允许同时运行多个独立的 Stata 会话，每个会话拥有独立的数据集、变量和宏。\n\n### 配置选项\n\n| 设置 | 描述 | 默认值 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| `stata-vscode.multiSession` | 启用多会话模式 | `true` |\n| `stata-vscode.maxSessions` | 最大并发会话数 | `100` |\n| `stata-vscode.sessionTimeout` | 会话空闲超时（秒） | `3600` |\n\n::: callout-warning\n每个会话需要约 200-300 MB RAM。请检查您的 Stata 许可证是否支持并发实例。\n:::\n\n## 输出过滤（节省 Token）\n\n### Compact 模式\n\n**设置**：`stata-vscode.resultDisplayMode`\n\n过滤内容：\n- 循环代码回显\n- 程序定义和 Mata 块\n- 命令回显和续行符\n\n### Token 限制\n\n**设置**：`stata-vscode.maxOutputTokens`\n\n- 默认：10000 tokens\n- 设为 0 表示无限制\n\n## 工作目录控制\n\n| 选项 | 描述 |\n|------|------|\n| `dofile` | 与 .do 文件相同目录（默认） |\n| `parent` | .do 文件的父目录 |\n| `workspace` | VS Code 工作区根目录 |\n\n**设置**：`stata-vscode.workingDirectory`\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":false,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":false,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":true,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":false,"code-overflow":"wrap","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":